 Advanced Text Extraction: Uses both direct extraction and OCR for PDFs
Intelligent Chunking: Splits documents into semantic chunks for better retrieval
Vector Search: Uses FAISS to find the most relevant document chunks
 LLM Integration: Leverages Claude LLM to generate accurate answers
 Caching: Optimizes performance with intelligent caching
 Progress Tracking: Shows real-time progress during document processing
 Error Handling: Robust error handling and user feedback

